categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: The individual was a male Weequay Jedi who served the Galactic Republic as a member of the Jedi Order during the Clone Wars. Around 20 BBY, the Jedi was present at the Temple during the Bombing of the Jedi Temple Hangar and he then attended the Funeral of the Jedi Temple bombing victims.

The Weequay male Jedi lived during the final decades of the Galactic Republic. The Jedi was sensitive to the Force and was brought to the Temple. He received training in the ways of the Jedi and became a Jedi.
Around 20 BBY, when the Jedi Temple was bombed by Dark Jedi Barriss Offee, the Jedi was present at the Temple. He then attended the Funeral of the Jedi Temple bombing victims.
